        <h2>SMART Goals & Benefits</h2>

        <p><strong>Goal 1:</strong> Reduce response time by 20% by Q3</p>
        <p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Minimizes user downtime, ensuring quicker resolutions</p>

        <p><strong>Goal 2:</strong> Increase First Contact Resolution by 25% by year-end</p>
        <p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Streamlines issue resolution, enhancing user experience</p>

        <p><strong>Goal 3:</strong> Decrease ticket backlog by 30% by mid-year</p>
        <p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Ensures prompt attention to new requests, improving satisfaction</p>

        <p><strong>Goal 4:</strong> Improve customer satisfaction score by 15% by year-end</p>
        <p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Encourages positive feedback, fostering trust plus confidence</p>

        <p><strong>Goal 5:</strong> Decrease incident resolution time by 20% by Q4</p>
        <p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Provides quicker solutions, reducing overall wait time</p>
